Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.95,0:23:08.41,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}息も言葉も
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.96,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}私を私にする魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.37,0:23:19.63,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}二人で手を伸ばしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.63,0:23:21.55,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}月にだって
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.55,0:23:26.05,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}届きそうな気がしてる
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.05,0:23:29.68,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}そう信じたい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.73,0:22:15.69,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}扼殺心緒
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.69,0:22:18.28,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}摒棄人慾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.28,0:22:21.61,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}早已成為慣例
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.53,0:22:27.45,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}無人在意
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.45,0:22:30.04,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}便無人在意
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.75,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}為何偏被你拾起
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.29,0:22:41.30,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}仿若難得一見的珍奇
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.30,0:22:46.76,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}被溫柔的手輕輕觸及
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.14,0:22:53.52,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}心門閉鎖後的斑斑鏽跡
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.52,0:23:00.90,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,1500)}由此漸漸痕跡消弭
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.78,0:23:04.95,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}無論是你的背影
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.95,0:23:08.41,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}呼吸 還是言語
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.96,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}都好似魔法 讓我成為自己
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.37,0:23:19.63,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}若我們一同伸出手臂
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.63,0:23:21.55,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}就連明月
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.55,0:23:26.05,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}都感覺觸手可及
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.05,0:23:29.68,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}我願如此相信
